<D>__{also here today is a marine biologist and research fellow from the oceanographic institute, matthew hooper. mr. hooper, what've you heard?}
<C>__{hooper}
<D>__{what i've heard and what i've seen are two different things. i believe there is a large great white shark carcharodon cacharias in the waters off this very beach, that he has killed and that he will kill again...}
