<B>__{angle on the beach}
<A>__{vaughn is in his shirtsleeves, having slipped out of his jacket. he mops his brow, and surveys the beachfront. at this moment, there's nobody swimming. he approaches a familiar selectman, nods hello, and squats beside him on the sand.}
<C>__{vaughn}
<D>__{why don't you get in the water?}
<C>__{selectman}
<D>__{i don't want to wash off my suntan lotion. i will get a burn...}
